{"id": "work_a765d3a0-2d16-5a47-842c-884c6b66c9a4", "title": "Observations of increasing carbon dioxide concentration in Earth\u2019s thermosphere", "sources": [{"source": "dtic", "id": "pub.1000442233"}], "last_updated": "2026-03-09T19:36:29.651561", "abstract": "Above an altitude of about 50\u2009km, carbon dioxide is the primary radiative cooling agent. Carbon dioxide and carbon monoxide mixing ratios derived from satellite-based solar occultation spectra document an estimated increase in global COx concentrations of about 23.5\u2009ppm per decade at an altitude of 101\u2009km.", "publication_date": "2012-11-11", "doi": "10.1038/ngeo1626", "url": "https://dtic.dimensions.ai/details/publication/pub.1000442233?and_facet_researcher=ur.011727670435.40", "citation_count": 0, "authors": [{"author_id": "author_b09fadee-2a62-529f-9093-6f677f53d113", "org_id": "org_4feff769-1869-5619-b908-61782a3c1367"}, {"author_id": "author_51430b7e-f057-5c82-938c-acf899dfa077", "org_id": "org_4feff769-1869-5619-b908-61782a3c1367"}, {"author_id": "author_baa4de7a-18d6-51ca-bcf6-edb09c063ea9", "org_id": "org_0e442424-567d-542f-adc4-2ffc7f374ead"}, {"author_id": "author_6e6ca175-4bba-5bce-93d9-0e4432d22939", "org_id": "org_4feff769-1869-5619-b908-61782a3c1367"}, {"author_id": "author_887444b3-31f2-5e52-8c87-7e1671375ca4", "org_id": "org_8b8083c2-32dd-5898-b6b9-b48bbf50c649"}], "orgs": [{"org_id": "org_4feff769-1869-5619-b908-61782a3c1367", "role": "affiliation"}, {"org_id": "org_0e442424-567d-542f-adc4-2ffc7f374ead", "role": "affiliation"}, {"org_id": "org_8b8083c2-32dd-5898-b6b9-b48bbf50c649", "role": "affiliation"}, {"org_id": "org_0c1265e8-3efb-52bb-989d-a580e5508237", "role": "affiliation"}], "topics": [{"topic_id": "topic_fd35fa6b-cba3-56dd-85e4-8b36bdd7a78e", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_a347ee21-80c4-5674-8b81-578e30479701", "score": 1.0}], "created_at": "2026-03-09T19:36:29.651561"}